data.description: Welcome to Your Forever Home in the Heart of Converse Judson's Football Country!  Nestled in the vibrant heart of a neighborhood renowned for its spirited community and unbeatable location near Judson High School-where Friday nights shine under stadium lights-this charming 4-bedroom, 2-bath traditional home awaits its next loving owners. Embrace the opportunity to be part of a town that lives and breathes high school football, offering a sense of belonging and community spirit that's hard to find elsewhere.  Stroll to Judson games and become part of the excitement, cheer on the local team, and enjoy the convenience of living near a landmark that brings the community together.  From the warm, inviting living spaces to the cozy family room, every corner tells a story of comfort and warmth.
